ME EVERYTHING.

21:38.384 --> 21:39.341
-OH REALLY?

21:39.472 --> 21:41.343
-WELL, WHAT ELSE
DID HE TELL YOU?

21:42.344 --> 21:43.519
-[PHONE RINGING]

