TOP LEFT DESK DRAWER.

21:58.229 --> 21:59.013
-WHAT IS IT?

21:59.143 --> 22:01.015
-WELL, THAT'S A SURPRISE.

22:01.145 --> 22:03.539
-SARA, YOU THANKED
ME ALREADY,

22:03.670 --> 22:05.062
