23:01.858 --> 23:03.469
-THESE, IT'S ALL
I CAN AFFORD.

23:03.599 --> 23:04.513
-WHAT IS THAT?

23:04.644 --> 23:06.254
-OH, THAT'S MY RAY WATCH.

23:06.385 --> 23:07.298
