YOU'RE GONNA BUILD YET?

23:14.088 --> 23:15.350
-UH, YEAH.

23:15.872 --> 23:16.786
-WELL?

23:16.917 --> 23:18.484
-IT'S A PROFESSIONAL SECRET.

23:19.180 --> 23:20.399
SURE BEATS THAT UH,

23:20.529 --> 23:21.487
