-[SCOFFING]

23:22.662 --> 23:23.880
IT'S A DOLPHIN, THANK YOU.

23:27.362 --> 23:28.755
-GEEZ, LOOK AT THAT KID!

23:31.279 --> 23:33.020
APRIL: WOW, THAT'S AMAZING!

23:33.150 --> 23:34.587
AND SHE LOOKS SO YOUNG!

23:34.717 --> 23:36.284
-MANNY: SHE'S A
KITE FLYING GENIUS!

23:36.893 --> 23:38.068
HEY, DO YOU THINK
SHE'S IN THE CONTEST

23:38.199 --> 23:39.853
OR JUST GOOFING AROUND?

23:39.983 --> 23:41.724
-[SIGHING] WELL, IF SHE'S
IN THE CONTEST, I'M TOAST.

23:42.377 --> 23:43.900
MY DOLPHIN CAN'T BEAT THAT.

23:44.031 --> 23:45.336
-AND NEITHER CAN MY SNAIL.

23:46.425 --> 23:47.295
-SNAIL?

23:47.817 --> 23:49.776
-YEAH, SNAIL.
LOOK.

23:52.039 --> 23:53.344
SUCKS, HUH?

23:53.475 --> 23:54.433
-PRETTY MUCH.

23:54.998 --> 23:55.869
WE'RE DOOMED.

23:57.261 --> 23:58.785
-HEY, I GOT AN IDEA, THOUGH.

23:58.915 --> 24:00.613
WE ONLY GOT ONE CHANCE.

24:00.743 --> 24:01.788
WE TEAM UP.

24:03.442 --> 24:05.008
-YOU AND ME TOGETHER?
-MANNY: YEAH.

24:06.183 --> 24:07.228
-OK.

24:07.358 --> 24:08.447
-ALL RIGHT!
-ALL RIGHT.

24:12.581 --> 24:14.148
-WOULD YOU LIKE SOME SUGAR?

24:14.278 --> 24:17.456
OH, OH NO NO THANK YOU,
NO SUGAR, JUST LEMON.

24:17.586 --> 24:19.414
I'M ON A DIET, BUT
DON'T TELL ANYBODY.

24:19.545 --> 24:20.894
-[LAUGHING]
SO AM I.

24:21.851 --> 24:23.070
-HELLO, SWEETHEART,

24:23.200 --> 24:24.419
YOU'RE SLEEPING SO WELL.

24:24.550 --> 24:26.508
SLEEP, SLEEP,
SLEEP, LITTLE BABY.

24:26.639 --> 24:27.814
ROCK A BYE BABY,

24:27.944 --> 24:29.032
IN THE TREE TOP.

24:29.163 --> 24:32.906
-[OMINOUS MUSIC]

24:33.689 --> 24:35.474
-OH MY, HERE
YOU GO, IRENE.

24:35.996 --> 24:37.345
-OH, THANK YOU, DEAR.

24:37.911 --> 24:39.347
I'M SO THIRSTY, TOO.

24:42.219 --> 24:43.743
THAT'S WONDERFUL.
-MMM.

24:43.873 --> 24:46.049
-I'M SO GLAD THIS IS
WORKING OUT WELL, SARA.

24:46.180 --> 24:47.834
-OH, WELL SO AM I.

24:48.356 --> 24:52.186
-EH, YOU KNOW, I HAVEN'T
BEEN A FULL TIME MOTHER

24:52.316 --> 24:54.405
IN A LONG LONG
TIME, AND IT'S,

24:54.928 --> 24:56.973
IT REALLY TAKES
A LOT OUT OF YOU.

24:57.104 --> 24:58.932
-I'M JUST SO GLAD
THAT I COULD HELP YOU.

24:59.062 --> 25:01.500
-YOU KNOW, SINCE MY
BOYS ARE ALL GROWN,

25:02.152 --> 25:05.025
I'VE FORGOTTEN HOW NICE IT WAS
TO BE AROUND A LITTLE BABY.

25:06.113 --> 25:08.245
AND HOW NICE IT IS
TO HAVE A NEW FRIEND.

25:08.855 --> 25:10.117
-OH, THAT'S SO SWEET.

25:10.247 --> 25:11.945
WELL, THANK YOU, IRENE.

25:12.075 --> 25:13.163
-OH MY.

25:14.991 --> 25:17.167
HAVE YOU EVER THOUGHT
ABOUT HAVING A BABY?

25:17.298 --> 25:18.604
-MM, GOSH.

25:19.256 --> 25:20.780
I'VE THOUGHT ABOUT IT, BUT,

25:21.432 --> 25:22.782
YOU KNOW, IT TAKES
THE RIGHT MAN

25:22.912 --> 25:25.045
AND WELL I GUESS
YOU KNOW THE STORY.

25:25.175 --> 25:26.742
-[LAUGHING]

25:26.873 --> 25:29.528
WELL, HERE'S TO THE RIGHT
MAN AND A BETTER STORY.

25:30.354 --> 25:31.660
-CHEERS.
-CHEERS.

25:34.707 --> 25:35.577
WHEW!

25:36.578 --> 25:38.972
OH BOY, I GUESS
ASHLEY WORE ME OUT

25:39.102 --> 25:40.843
THAN I REMEMBERED,
I'M SO TIRED.

25:40.974 --> 25:42.802
-YOU KNOW THOSE BABIES, THEY
JUST KEEP GOING ON FOREVER.

25:42.932 --> 25:44.020
IT'S KIND OF LIKE THAT UM,

25:44.630 --> 25:46.196
WHAT IS IT, THAT BUNNY
IN THE COMMERCIAL

25:46.327 --> 25:47.458
