AND GOING AND GOING.

25:47.589 --> 25:48.590
-[LAUGHING]

25:48.721 --> 25:50.461
YOU'RE SO RIGHT.
YEAH.

25:50.984 --> 25:52.594
-WHY DON'T YOU
JUST TAKE A NAP,

25:52.725 --> 25:54.640
AND I'LL SIT HERE AND
I'LL WATCH ASHLEY?

25:55.858 --> 25:57.599
-OH, I'M SORRY,
MAYBE I SHOULD,

25:58.557 --> 25:59.819
I, I'M TERRIBLY SLEEPY.

25:59.949 --> 26:00.994
-COME ON, COME ON.

26:01.603 --> 26:02.517
LAY DOWN.

26:02.648 --> 26:04.345
KICK YOUR FEET UP, COME ON.

26:12.353 --> 26:16.096
-[OMINOUS MUSIC]

26:20.709 --> 26:21.928
-[BABY CRYING]

26:26.149 --> 26:27.020
-HI.

26:29.500 --> 26:31.720
