TO SLEEP THROUGH IT.

26:35.506 --> 26:36.551
WELL, YOU KNOW IT'S,

26:36.682 --> 26:37.813
IT'S BEEN A LONG
TIME FOR HER

26:37.944 --> 26:39.075
AND BABIES ARE A HANDFUL.

26:40.163 --> 26:41.774
WHY DON'T WE JUST
LET HER SLEEP HERE,

26:41.904 --> 26:44.472
