SLEEP WITH ME

26:44.603 --> 26:45.516
UP IN MY ROOM TONIGHT?

26:46.474 --> 26:47.344
-GREAT.

26:48.476 --> 26:49.346
GLAD YOU'RE HERE.

26:50.521 --> 26:52.785
I'LL JUST TAKE HER
UPSTAIRS NOW, OK?

27:05.798 --> 27:07.364
MITCH, MITCH, WAKE UP.

27:07.495 --> 27:08.539
-WHAT'S THE MATTER?

27:08.670 --> 27:10.498
-WELL, YOU WERE
CALLIN' MY NAME.

27:11.107 --> 27:12.065
YOU WOKE ME UP.

27:12.195 --> 27:13.675
-I DID?
-YEAH.

27:14.981 --> 27:16.809
I GUESS IT WAS JUST A DREAM.

27:18.637 --> 27:19.594
-YEAH.

27:19.725 --> 27:20.987
-BUT IT'S KIND OF NICE TO,

27:21.117 --> 27:22.771
TO BE IN A HANDSOME
MAN'S DREAM.

27:25.208 --> 27:26.122
-I, I DON'T REMEMBER.

27:27.167 --> 27:28.559
-IS THERE ANYTHING THAT YOU,

27:28.690 --> 27:29.996
YOU NEED OR,

27:30.649 --> 27:32.259
IS THERE ANYTHING
THAT YOU WANT?

27:33.652 --> 27:35.958
-NO, NO I'M FINE.

27:36.089 --> 27:37.220
-ARE YOU SURE?

27:37.351 --> 27:38.482
-YEAH, YEAH, I'M SURE,

27:38.613 --> 27:39.483
WHY DON'T YOU JUST UH,

27:40.310 --> 27:41.094
GO BACK TO BED, SARA.

27:41.224 --> 27:42.095
-OK.

27:43.662 --> 27:45.141
-YOU KNOW, IF YOU
CHANGE YOUR MIND,

27:45.272 --> 27:47.491
I'M, I'M JUST RIGHT
DOWN THAT HALL.

27:51.191 --> 27:52.714
DON'T LET THE BED BUGS BITE.

27:53.236 --> 27:54.107
GOOD NIGHT.

28:11.298 --> 28:14.083
-[LAUGHING]

28:20.481 --> 28:21.525
MANNY: LOOK OUT!
WE'RE GONNA CRASH!

28:21.656 --> 28:22.744
APRIL: OH NO!

28:29.316 --> 28:30.186
-PATHETIC.

28:34.147 --> 28:35.626
THE SECOND PLACE WINNER...

28:37.890 --> 28:39.848
NICE JOB.
-SECOND PLACE?

28:39.979 --> 28:41.328
-NEWMIE: HERE'S YOUR TROPHY.
WOW, THAT
GIRL'S SPECTACULAR.

28:41.458 --> 28:43.547
WAIT A MINUTE, HOW, WHO
COULD POSSIBLY BEAT HER?

28:43.678 --> 28:45.375
-AND FIRST PLACE.

28:46.376 --> 28:48.814
-WOW, I THOUGHT
THE GIRL WAS GOOD.

28:48.944 --> 28:50.641
-YEAH, THIS WAS A
PIECE OF ARTWORK.

28:50.772 --> 28:52.469
WHOEVER DID THIS
IS A PROFESSIONAL.

28:55.081 --> 28:56.604
-NEWMIE: HEY,
GOOD JOB TODAY.

28:57.561 --> 28:58.737
HERE'S YOUR TROPHY.

28:58.867 --> 28:59.738
-THANKS.

29:00.826 --> 29:05.439
-[CHEERING]

29:08.659 --> 29:10.052
-SO YOU GOT
BEAT, NO BIGGIE.

29:10.183 --> 29:11.140
-YEAH, BY KIDS.

29:12.402 --> 29:13.969
