WIN THAT TROPHY.

29:14.622 --> 29:15.797
-WELL, YOU DID WIN A TROPHY.

29:16.406 --> 29:17.886
THE LOSER'S TROPHY
FOR LAST PLACE.

29:18.017 --> 29:19.583
-GREAT, LAST PLACE.

29:19.714 --> 29:21.585
GEE, HOW EMBARRASSING
IS THAT, HUH?

29:21.716 --> 29:23.239
-YEAH, NOTHING GETS
MORE EMBARRASSING

29:23.370 --> 29:25.589
THAN LOSING TO A 12 YEAR
OLD AND AN EIGHT YEAR OLD.

29:26.329 --> 29:27.200
-OH YEAH?

29:28.201 --> 29:30.638
WELL, CONGRATULATIONS.

29:34.337 --> 29:36.252
WHY DON'T YOU GUYS TAKE THAT
HOME AND KEEP IT POLISHED UP?

29:41.257 --> 29:43.042
-MAN: THEY BLEW IT DOWN,
THEY SHOULD'VE KICKED!

29:55.445 --> 29:56.403
-HI!

29:57.230 --> 29:58.013
-SEE YA.
-BYE.

29:58.144 --> 29:59.623
-HI!

29:59.754 --> 30:01.321
-AS PROMISED, ONE
DELICIOUS HOMEMADE LUNCH.

30:01.451 --> 30:03.279
DELIVERED TO YOUR
DOOR. [LAUGHING]

30:05.499 --> 30:07.196
WHAT'S WRONG?

30:07.327 --> 30:10.983
-SARA, MY MOTHER AND
I THANK YOU VERY MUCH

30:11.113 --> 30:14.508
FOR EVERYTHING YOU'VE DONE
FOR US AND FOR ASHLEY, BUT..

30:15.161 --> 30:16.597
-BUT WHAT?

30:17.511 --> 30:19.774
-SARA, IT'S NOT WORKING
OUT LIKE WE HOPED.

30:21.036 --> 30:22.342
-ARE YOU FIRING ME?

30:23.038 --> 30:24.474
-WE'RE LETTING YOU GO,

30:24.605 --> 30:25.824
BUT WE'RE GONNA GIVE YOU
A FULL MONTH'S SALARY.

30:26.433 --> 30:27.782
-SARA: NO!

30:28.435 --> 30:30.306
-REALLY, WE'RE,
WE'RE VERY SORRY.

30:30.437 --> 30:31.307
-SORRY?

30:31.830 --> 30:32.787
YOU'RE SORRY?

30:33.353 --> 30:35.181
YOU CAN'T DO THIS TO ME.

30:36.051 --> 30:37.400
-YOU CAN FIND ANOTHER JOB.

30:38.749 --> 30:40.012
-I WON'T GO.

30:40.751 --> 30:41.622
-SARA, PLEASE.

30:41.752 --> 30:43.319
-DON'T TOUCH ME!

30:44.451 --> 30:46.496
I WON'T LET YOU
DO THIS TO ME.

30:46.627 --> 30:48.324
YOU CAN'T DO THIS TO ME!

30:51.066 --> 30:52.328
HELP! STOP!

30:52.459 --> 30:53.852
-STOP IT, STOP IT.

30:53.982 --> 30:55.766
-DON'T HIT ME [MUMBLES] .

30:55.897 --> 30:57.203
-HELP, PLEASE!
MITCH: STOP IT, STOP IT.

30:57.333 --> 30:58.900
-SARA: PLEASE DON'T HIT ME!
-COME ON!

31:01.511 --> 31:02.382
-HEY!

31:03.557 --> 31:04.863
[GRUNTING]

31:07.300 --> 31:08.910
-YOU LIKE TO PICK
ON WOMEN, TOUGH GUY?

31:10.956 --> 31:12.522
-[MITCH GROANING]

31:12.653 --> 31:14.698
-HEY, BUDDY, YOU SHOULD
USE YOUR MANNERS.

31:14.829 --> 31:15.743
-OH!

31:21.314 --> 31:22.663
-WOMAN: ARE YOU OK?

31:23.185 --> 31:25.231
-MAN: WOW, MAN, YOU, MAYBE
WE SHOULD GET YOU TO A DOCTOR.

31:25.840 --> 31:27.755
-[MITCH PANTING]

31:28.625 --> 31:29.757
-WOMAN: WE'RE JUST HELPING.

31:29.888 --> 31:30.845
-MAN: TAKE IT EASY, MAN.

31:35.850 --> 31:38.548
-HELLO MY LITTLE ANGEL.

31:38.679 --> 31:41.508
OH, YOU'RE SUCH A
SWEETHEART, YES YOU ARE.

31:41.638 --> 31:44.424
NOW LISTEN, NANA'S
GONNA TAKE A SHOWER,

31:44.554 --> 31:46.774
AND THEN, THEN WE'LL
GO FOR A WALK, OK?

31:47.601 --> 31:48.689
YOU BE A GOOD GIRL.

31:48.819 --> 31:50.299
YOU BE A GOOD GIRL NOW.

31:50.430 --> 31:52.127
PEEK-A-BOO. [LAUGHING]

31:53.085 --> 31:54.913
OH DEAR, DEAR, DEAR.

31:56.827 --> 31:58.046
-[BABY COOING]

32:06.489 --> 32:10.929
-[WATER RUNNING]

32:17.500 --> 32:18.545
-[BABY COOING]

32:26.814 --> 32:27.902
-SARA: OH, SWEETHEART,

32:28.816 --> 32:30.252
OH, MY BABY.

32:30.992 --> 32:32.472
HI, MY ANGEL.

32:33.212 --> 32:36.389
HI, HI, BABY.

32:36.519 --> 32:37.651
LET'S GO,

32:38.260 --> 32:39.131
COME ON.

32:39.261 --> 32:40.175
UP WE GO.

