34:53.786 --> 34:54.875
OH!

34:55.440 --> 34:58.487
OH! DARLING,
THERE YOU ARE!

34:58.618 --> 35:01.751
OH MY GOODNESS
GRACIOUS, YOU'RE BACK.

35:02.926 --> 35:07.888
-YEAH, HI, IT'S OK, IT'S OK.
-MITCH, WHAT'S THAT?

35:10.934 --> 35:13.763
YES, YOU'RE HOME, YOU'RE
SAFE AGAIN, MY DARLING.

35:20.205 --> 35:21.989
-IF SHE EVER TOUCHES
ASHLEY AGAIN...

35:33.479 --> 35:34.436
-HEY, APRIL.

35:35.176 --> 35:36.569
-HI TODD.

35:36.699 --> 35:37.700
-I WOUND UP GOING TO
THAT KITE FLYING CONTEST

35:37.831 --> 35:38.919
MY UNCLE SPONSORED.

35:39.049 --> 35:39.833
-OH REALLY?

35:39.963 --> 35:41.226
-I DIDN'T SEE YOU THERE.

35:41.356 --> 35:43.184
-I LIKE TO KEEP
A LOW PROFILE.

35:44.098 --> 35:45.578
SO WHAT DID YOU THINK?

35:45.708 --> 35:47.536
-YOU AND MANNY WEREN'T
AS BAD AS I EXPECTED.

35:47.667 --> 35:49.190
-[LAUGHING] WE
TOOK LAST PLACE.

35:49.321 --> 35:50.496
-BUT YOU CARED
ENOUGH TO TRY.

35:50.626 --> 35:51.932
THAT'S THE
IMPORTANT THING.

35:52.062 --> 35:53.673
-WELL, I HOPE WE
SET A GOOD EXAMPLE.

35:53.803 --> 35:55.153
-IT WASN'T JUST YOU.

35:55.762 --> 35:57.720
