GAVE UP HOPE.

36:03.465 --> 36:06.425
KINDA GOT ME THINKING THAT
MAYBE I DON'T HAVE IT SO BAD.

36:07.469 --> 36:08.644
-WELL, HE'S RIGHT.

36:08.775 --> 36:10.255
YOU SHOULD NEVER
GIVE UP HOPE.

36:10.820 --> 36:12.344
I MEAN, WHO KNOWS?

36:12.474 --> 36:14.607
MAYBE SOMEDAY THEY WILL
FIND A CURE FOR DIABETES.

36:14.737 --> 36:16.739
THEN YOU WON'T HAVE TO GET
INSULIN SHOTS EVERY DAY

36:16.870 --> 36:18.001
AND YOU COULD EAT
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

36:18.132 --> 36:19.307
-THAT SOUNDS GOOD TO ME.

36:19.960 --> 36:21.091
-WELL, LISTEN.

36:21.222 --> 36:22.658
I GOT ONE
QUESTION FOR YOU.

36:22.789 --> 36:24.530
WHAT ELSE DID YOUR
UNCLE SAY ABOUT ME?

36:25.052 --> 36:26.140
-I PROMISED NOT TO TELL.

36:26.271 --> 36:27.446
-TODD?

36:27.576 --> 36:29.317
-HE SWORE ME TO SILENCE!

36:29.448 --> 36:30.710
-TODD, GET BACK HERE!

36:30.840 --> 36:32.668
-[BOTH LAUGHING]

36:51.339 --> 36:55.169
-[OMINOUS MUSIC]

37:08.138 --> 37:09.052
