38:39.404 --> 38:41.188
-WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

38:41.319 --> 38:44.757
-THE REAL SARA
CHAPMAN WAS A NANNY

38:44.887 --> 38:47.107
TO YOU AND YOUR
HUSBAND'S DAUGHTER, DANA.

38:49.109 --> 38:52.634
LAST SUMMER, YOUR
HUSBAND DIVORCED YOU,

38:52.765 --> 38:55.637
AND MARRIED THE
NANNY, SARA CHAPMAN.

38:55.768 --> 38:57.335
YOUR NAME IS CARLY.

38:57.944 --> 39:00.076
-NO, THAT IS A LIE,
THAT IS NOT TRUE.

39:00.207 --> 39:01.600
-YOU'VE GOT SOME
EMOTIONAL PROBLEMS,

39:01.730 --> 39:03.689
YOU WENT INTO THE HOSPITAL.

39:03.819 --> 39:06.474
THE COURT AWARDED CUSTODY OF
YOUR DAUGHTER TO YOUR HUSBAND.

39:06.605 --> 39:08.998
NOW THAT BOAT FIRE WAS NO
ACCIDENT, WAS IT, CARLY?

39:09.129 --> 39:10.260
-OH, MITCH!

39:10.391 --> 39:11.392
-IT WAS NO
ACCIDENT, WAS IT?

39:11.523 --> 39:12.350
-NO!

39:14.134 --> 39:16.266
-NOW, TELL ME,
WHERE'S MY MOTHER?

39:16.397 --> 39:19.139
-[CRYING] DON'T LEAVE ME
PLEASE DON'T LEAVE ME,

39:19.269 --> 39:20.706
I JUST WANT YOU TO
LOVE ME, THAT'S ALL,

39:20.836 --> 39:22.098
I WANT YOU TO LOVE ME!

39:22.229 --> 39:24.057
I DON'T KNOW!
-WHERE'S MY MOTHER?

39:24.187 --> 39:25.450
-I DON'T KNOW!
-WHERE?

39:25.580 --> 39:27.756
-MITCH! MITCH!

39:27.887 --> 39:30.368
-I DON'T KNOW!
-MOM! MOM!

39:33.109 --> 39:34.850
-[SCREAMING]

39:34.981 --> 39:36.330
